案，內蒙古近期共確診4宗鼠疫病例。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20191128/mobile/bkn-20191128093336022-1128_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20191128%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20191128093336022-1128_00952_001.html&d=iBLSwy1tqwhlDNpwtuM9DaCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=a16df0de\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20191128/mobile/bkn-20191128093336022-1128_00952_001.html</a>"}]}